Package com.viaoa.jfc.report

OAReports for creating custom reports and print forms, with binding and templates that use OAModels.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
OAHTMLCertificate This uses HTML that has a (hi-res) background image to create a certificate the size of the background image.
OAHTMLCertificatePdf This uses HTML that has a (hi-res) background image to create a certificate the size of the background image.
OAHTMLConverter Converts html text with custom properties and processing tags into pure html text, by using a supplied list of values to plug into the text.
OAHTMLReport Creates a printable report, that uses html as the data to create a report with heading and footing.
OAHTMLTextPaneFooter Component used for report footers.
OAHTMLTextPaneHeader Component used for report headers.
OAPdf Generate pdf documents, using printable.
OAReport Creates a report that contains a Header, Footer and Detail.
